<p><strong>对论文的贡献：</strong></p><ul><li> Gavin Leech：技术作家</li><li>Monte MacDiarmid：进行了额外的实验</li><li>Lisa Thiergart：帮助管理项目</li><li>Alex Turner：协调工作并获得资金，提供反馈，组织项目</li><li>大卫·乌德尔：最初制作</li></ul><ol class="footnotes" role="doc-endnotes"><li class="footnote-item" role="doc-endnote" id="fnoutccz5xmqc"> <span class="footnote-back-link"><sup><strong><a href="#fnrefoutccz5xmqc">^</a></strong></sup></span><div class="footnote-content"><p>完整流程：</p><p>对于 OpenWebText 随机样本中的每个文档<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="d_i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.003em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">d</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，我们首先计算与婚礼相关的单词（&#39;wedding&#39;、&#39;weddings&#39;、&#39;wed&#39;、&#39;marry&#39;、&#39;married&#39;、&#39;marriage&#39;、&#39;bride&#39; 的频率, &#39;新郎&#39;, &#39;蜜月&#39;), fw( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="d_i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.003em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">d</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ).任何包含 >; 0 个与婚礼相关的单词的文档都被视为与婚礼相关。我们随机抽取 30 万份文档——一半与婚礼相关，一半无关。执行的唯一预处理是删除空字符序列。使用 Punkt 分词器 (Strunk 2013) 将每个文档分割成句子<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="s_j \in d_i"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">s</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">j</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∈</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.003em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">d</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">i</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</p><p>对于每个结果句子，我们计算未修改的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="M"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.081em;">M</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> -baseline 和修改的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="M"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.081em;">M</span></span></spa